{
  "texts": [
    "8 We analyze the quality of our categories in §6.",
    "In this section we study the effect of new knowledge in the fine-tuning dataset D on performance.",
    "To isolate this effect, we vary the proportion of Unknown examples in D, while controlling for other factors.",
    "Specifically, we fix |D| and create variants of D with X% of Unknown and (100 -X)% Known examples (full details in §E).",
    "We treat the Known categories collectively (see Figure 2a), and provide a per-category analysis in §5."
  ]
}